  • Get ready to spread a little happiness with every wear!

    Shikako the Happy Avocado Hoodie is the perfect gift for anyone who loves avocados and cute characters. Shikako is a cheerful avocado who likes to explore the world and make new friends. Whether you want to wear it yourself or give it to someone special, Shikako the Happy Avocado Hoodie will make you smile and feel warm inside.

    This kawaii hoodie is available in 13 colors and 5 different sizes in 5 different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below.     It is best to measure your chest and length, and then choose a size according to the result to simplify the various international measurements.
